   No.  Well N is ok but N doesn't matter.

>  There are 5 blocks with
>76 experiment items.

   So S would be 76.

>  Each item takes 17 DMDX item lines

   So G would be 17, assuming you want those 17 items to not be moved with 
respect to each other.

>(including the
>0 and 800 items) and each block is followed by a rest. I have 10
>practice items that all have the same item number (7). I've set n=6460
